<div><head>張詮南燕書</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.2">慕容德以右僕射封嵩為左僕射，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.3">尚書韓為右僕射。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.4">時嵩並年三十，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.5">又以嵩弟融為西中郎將，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.6">𧨳弟軌為東中郎將。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.7">嵩等俱拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.8">帝臨軒、詔令四人同入。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.9">嵩等升殿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.10">方謝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.11">帝顧曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.12">「躍二龍於長衢騁雙驥於千里。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.13">朝野榮之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-1a.14">《初學記》十、《御覽》三百十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-2a.2">德將死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-2a.3">以超為皇太子。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-2a.4">超，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-2a.5">德兄北海王納之子。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-2a.6">慕容納沈靜深邃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-2a.7">外訥內敏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1311_CHANT_001-2a.8">《御覽》四百六十四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
